aces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3781d5e46629c22eac3d9e9fb834937436a520f","tid":316513,"uid":79866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T20:56:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雙子男係咪好難捉摸？</blockquote><br />\n我自己都覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好容易會唔鐘意一個人 or 有好感<br />\n但可以好快冇野"},{"pid":"54cc61b6c23b1d8d1907d195bf645f832b890478","tid":316513,"uid":360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T22:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男朋友係雙子 我係天蠍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真 唔夾一定有 嗌交嗰d實有<br />\n<br />\n對我黎講 雙子真係真係好專一 當佢認定左既人佢就會中意都底<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">只可惜嗰個唔係我</span></span><br />\n同埋佢地雙重人格得好緊 係出面大癲大肺 好易同人fd同人熟 但其實內心好脆弱 好易夜晚自己一個喊<br />\n<br />\n不過8月我地就3年啦<br />\n由頭兩年LD 同岩岩一年同居 基本上都慣左呢個人<br />\n咁岩我地去完日本 我返左英國 佢返香港<br />\n只係3日我已經好掛住佢 開始亂諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌同你差唔多<br />\n我同我女朋友都係英國讀<br />\n我係雙子 佢係天蠍<br />\n你講雙子既野我都中哂咁濟<br />\n成日都比女朋友話我唔成熟同好懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我要返工返到屋企已經好攰 仲要煮飯洗衫執屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋會成日發細路仔脾氣<br />\n好似岩岩我同緊同事食飯 佢會要我同佢講完電話先 成餐飯就咁冷落左個同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我又大佢兩年呢"},{"pid":"1f89472c833548147231b438e1886378109ca59a","tid":316513,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T12:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0b8dd32cc7a53ddbe1c941e525e8875c4bbcb0","tid":316513,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T12:28:26.000Z","msg":"呢度有 一齊左一年幾 已散"}]}